{
  "stem": "24212.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I could see parts-- you know, like an inch here, an inch there-- of the road from the railroad station to the chimney.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And on several occasions, the time coincided that I was on my cot and looked out, and there were groups of people in dress-- you know, I mean, in clothing-- coming from the station, going to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that is the reason why I'm saying this-- and many other things that we observed, of course, in Auschwitz-- is the reason that the best testimonials about the Holocaust, about confirming yes, there was a Holocaust and none of this idiotic nonsense that there was no Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, the lunatic fringe is here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We are the best of witnesses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because we are the so-called objective witnesses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We are not Jewish, but we saw it, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Not mentioning the Sonderkommando, which sometimes was Jewish and sometimes was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And some of them survived and wrote their memoirs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So this lunatic fringe, and I thought that by now they stop, but they don't.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was block four, but I wouldn't swear to it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very low number.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think the Lidice women were three, we were four, and the Jews were five.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I went back to Auschwitz, and I was absolutely lost-- Birkenau, really, not, not Auschwitz-- because the barracks don't stand anywhere.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had to take them down, so they say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they have one or two of those-- we call them blocks and now they call them barracks-- left.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went in and it didn't look like my barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was lots of brick work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, there is lots of brick work in those sample blocks.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
